bpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shiann_Salmon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the heats of the men's 400m competition, which is scheduled to start at 12:05 pm Jamaica time, national champion Deandre Watkins, Sean Bailey and Jevaughn Powell are set to participate in the event for Jamaica.\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2160, \"end\": 2167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0299511290633872e-16, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 2209, \"end\": 2220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Bailey\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.0212074856877295e-13, \"text\": \"Sean Bailey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Bailey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Bailey\"}, {\"begin\": 2234, \"end\": 2240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Powell\", \"score\": 0.9999999987694537, \"rank\": 1.2124591958562961e-09, \"text\": \"Powell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Powell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Powell\"}, {\"begin\": 2281, \"end\": 2288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0299511290633872e-16, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shericka Jackson leaves training at Complexe Sportif de L'lle Des Vannes in France on July 30, 2024.\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2291, \"end\": 2307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shericka_Jackson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shericka Jackson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpe